{"article_id":"07hh0oGbL2SVlNN1","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"North Korea just successfully tested an intercontinental ballistic missile , one of its most audacious moves yet","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"- and a vivid reminder","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"that Pyongyang seems determined to test","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"whether President Donald Trump is willing to turn his tough talk about the country ' s nuclear threat into action .","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"The Hwasong-14 flew for 37 minutes ,","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"according to US Pacific Command ,","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"and traveled about 578 miles .","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"It didn ' t go as far","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"as it could","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"because it was shot at a high trajectory ,","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"likely to ensure","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"it didn ' t make another country believe","depth":11},{"id":12,"text":"it was being attacked .","depth":11},{"id":13,"text":"The projectile eventually landed in the sea between Japan and North Korea ,","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"but analysts believe","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"it could have traveled as far as 4,200 miles","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"if it had been fired with an actual intent","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"to strike a target in case of conflict .","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"In response , the US and South Korea held a military exercise within 10 miles of the demilitarized zone","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"that separates North Korea from its neighbor .","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"Meanwhile , Secretary of State Rex Tillerson called for \" global action \"","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"to counter North Korea ,","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"while China and Russia asked for a \" double suspension \" of the military exercise and North Korea ' s weapons program .","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"Based on the global reaction ,","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"the missile test was clearly a big deal .","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"That ' s because another of the caveats about North Korea","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"- primarily that it didn ' t have an intercontinental ballistic missile , or ICBM ,","depth":12},{"id":27,"text":"that could hit the mainland United States -","depth":12},{"id":28,"text":"are steadily disappearing .","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"\" That range would not be enough","depth":12},{"id":30,"text":"to reach the lower 48 states or the large islands of Hawaii ,","depth":12},{"id":31,"text":"but would allow it to reach all of Alaska , \"","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"wrote David Wright , co-director of the Union of Concerned Scientists .","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"And , down the line , this test could be seen as a stepping stone to an even more threatening development .","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"\" Even if this is a 7,000-km-range missile ,","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"a 10,000-km-range missile","depth":13},{"id":36,"text":"that can hit New York","depth":13},{"id":37,"text":"isn ' t far off , \"","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"Jeffrey Lewis , director of the East Asia Nonproliferation Program at the Middlebury Institute of International Studies , told the New York Times .","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"What ' s still not clear is if North Korea has the ability","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"to miniaturize a nuclear weapon","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"so it could be placed on the tip of the missile ,","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"and ,","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"even if it can ,","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"if the missile could reach the US","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"and still detonate .","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"However , Lewis told me in April","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"that North Korea was only about five years away from being able to do that .","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"Back in January , North Korean leader Kim Jong Un said","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"that his country was close to testing an ICBM .","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"President Donald Trump promised","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"that it wouldn ' t happen ,","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"which could raise the pressure on the administration to do something","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"beyond tweeting out words of disapproval .","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"And that ' s what ' s important to keep in mind :","depth":6},{"id":55,"text":"No matter what Trump has said ,","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"or the pressure","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"the US , China , and others try to place on North Korea ,","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"Kim continues to test missiles","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"that could harm America and its allies .","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"This was not the kind of projectile","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"Americans are used to hearing about on July Fourth .","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"Trump ' s strategy","depth":7},{"id":63,"text":"for containing North Korea","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"is to have China lean on Pyongyang","depth":7},{"id":65,"text":"to knock off its aggressive behavior .","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"The problem is Beijing has given no sign","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"that it ' s willing to pressure its neighbor , a major Chinese trading partner .","depth":7},{"id":68,"text":"That ' s left Trump ,","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"who famously said","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"he changed his mind about North Korea after a 10-minute conversation with Chinese President Xi Jinping ,","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"to take a swing at Beijing .","depth":7},{"id":72,"text":"North Korea has just launched another missile .","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"Does this guy have anything better to do with his life ?","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"Hard to believe that South Korea .....","depth":7},{"id":75,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"July 4 , 2017","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":".... and Japan will put up with this much longer .","depth":7},{"id":79,"text":"Perhaps China will put a heavy move on North Korea","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"and end this nonsense once and for all !","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"- Donald J. Trump","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"( @ realDonaldTrump )","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"July 4 , 2017","depth":7},{"id":84,"text":"As my colleague Zeeshan Aleem noted ,","depth":7},{"id":85,"text":"the Trump administration has slapped sanctions on China","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"because it has yet to curtail North Korea ' s missile program .","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"\" While we will continue to seek international cooperation on North Korea ,","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"the United States is sending an emphatic message across the globe","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"that we will not hesitate to take action against persons , companies , and financial institutions","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"who enable this regime , \"","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"Treasury Secretary Steve Mnuchin said in a June 29 statement on the sanctions ,","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"clearly alluding to China .","depth":7},{"id":93,"text":"Then again , there was little reason","depth":7},{"id":94,"text":"to believe","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"that China was going to step up","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"and put immense pressure on North Korea","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"to stop its program ,","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"in part because it fears","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"a collapse of the regime would lead to millions of desperate refugees","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"streaming over its border .","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"\" That ' s because Beijing has a vested interest in a stable North Korea","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"- and will drag its heels as much","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"as it can","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"on measures","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"that could destabilize the country , \"","depth":11},{"id":106,"text":"wrote Aleem .","depth":8},{"id":107,"text":"But the administration rightly feels","depth":6},{"id":108,"text":"there ' s a growing sense of urgency","depth":7},{"id":109,"text":"to quell the threat ,","depth":7},{"id":110,"text":"especially since North Korea ' s missile program has improved very quickly recently .","depth":6},{"id":111,"text":"\" In the past three years , North Korea has launched more major missiles than in the three previous decades combined , \"","depth":8},{"id":112,"text":"noted the Wall Street Journal .","depth":8},{"id":113,"text":"This latest test is now the gold standard for North Korea .","depth":7},{"id":114,"text":"There is some good news :","depth":7},{"id":115,"text":"The United States successfully pulled off its own test in May","depth":8},{"id":116,"text":"that showed","depth":10},{"id":117,"text":"it is capable","depth":10},{"id":118,"text":"of stopping one of these missiles","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"before it hits American territory .","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"Still , the US anti-ICBM system has yet to be tested against the real thing -","depth":7},{"id":121,"text":"and most hope","depth":8},{"id":122,"text":"the US never has to do that .","depth":8},{"id":123,"text":"So for now , there is no real reason for complete panic .","depth":6},{"id":124,"text":"But there is reason","depth":7},{"id":125,"text":"to worry","depth":8},{"id":126,"text":"that one of the most dangerous and unpredictable regimes on earth is coming closer and closer to being able to hit major American cities .","depth":8},{"id":127,"text":"Trump is mired in an array of scandals and crises of his own making .","depth":2},{"id":128,"text":"This is one","depth":3},{"id":129,"text":"where the culprit is someone else -","depth":4},{"id":130,"text":"and where the solution remains painfully elusive .","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":261,"left":257,"right":260,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":257,"left":202,"right":256,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":202,"left":178,"right":201,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":178,"l